MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Add a new getter, get_io_tlb_mem, to help select the io_tlb_mem struct.
The restricted DMA pool is preferred if available.

Signed-off-by: Claire Chang <tientzu@chromium.org>
